'''Tenno Shrine''' (天皇神社) is a [[:en:Shinto shrine|shrine]] located in [[:en:Shiga Prefecture|Shiga Prefecture]][[:en:Ōtsu|Otsu City]].

== Geography ==
[[:en:West Japan Railway Company|JR]][[:en:Wani Station|Wani Station]] is located approximately 1.1 [[:en:Kilometre|kilometer]] to the southwest <ref name=":0">{{Cite web|和書|url=https://www.biwako-visitors.jp/spot/detail/158|title=天皇神社{{!}}滋賀県観光情報|accessdate=2020-04-22|publisher=びわこビジターズビューロー|date=2015-06-23}}</ref>, and a 10‐minute walk away <ref name=":1">{{Cite web|和書|url=http://nishioumi.ct-net.com/00-05.shtml|title=歴史散歩・和邇天皇神社　和邇祭り|accessdate=2020-04-22|publisher=京都新聞西近江販売所連合|year=2000|month=05}}</ref>. It is situated along the roadside of Ryūka Crossing (present‐day {{ill|Shiga Prefecture Route 311, Tokochu Shiga Line|ja|滋賀県道311号途中志賀線|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiga Prefecture Route 311, Tokochu Shiga Line|qq=}}) {{Sfn|滋賀県教育委員会事務局文化財保護課|2019|p=20}}. It is about 5 minutes from {{ill|Kosai Road|ja|湖西道路|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kosai Road|qq=}} ([[:en:Japan National Route 161|National Route 161]]) {{ill|Wani IC|ja|和迩インターチェンジ|lt=Wani IC|lt_ja=和邇IC|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wani IC|qq=}} <ref name=":2">{{Cite web|和書|url=https://otsu.or.jp/thingstodo/spot213|title=天皇神社|accessdate=2020-04-22|publisher=びわ湖大津観光協会}}</ref>.

